      %h4 General
      %ul
        %li
          The entry fee is $50 per pool entry. Payment is due upon registration.  Zelle is accepted.
        %li
          The commissioner has final say with any dispute.
        %li
          The pool will not be split prior to week 16. By entering the contest, you agree to play through week 15 or until the pool ends.
        %li
          The commissioner will not share any entrant contact information to anyone.  
        %li
          In the event of a website malfunction of any kind, the commissioner has final say regarding that week's picks.
        %li
          %span.red If you choose a game that is canceled or rescheduled to another week, your pick will be defaulted to the Monday night home team.
        %li
          %span.red In the event your pick cannot be defaulted to MNF, your pick will be defaulted to the Sunday Night Home team. If your pick cannot be defaulted to SNF, the commissioner will choose a default game for that week.
        %li
          Choose one team from the current week's NFL schedule that you think will win. If your team wins, you continue in the pool for another week. If your team loses or ties, you are eliminated from the pool. The pool will continue until there is one remaining entrant or the end of the regular season. However, any time after week 15 all remaining entrants may split the pool if 100% of the remaining entrants agree to split.
        %li
          In the event that all entrants are eliminated in one week, the pool will be divided amongst those entrants.
        %li
          In the event that there are remaining entrants at the end of the regular season, the pool will end and winners will be paid.
        %li
          100% of the money received less $580 will be paid to the winner(s).
        %li
          $80 will be paid to Heroku and GoDaddy for hosting fees
        %li
          $500 will be paid to the web developers for their website responsibilities.
        %li
          The commissioner is awarded four free pool entries for the administrative duties associated with the pool.
        %li
          The web developers are awarded four free pool entries for their administrative duties associated with the KO Pool.
  .row
    .col-sm-12
      %h4 DEADLINES - Submitting your weekly pick.
      %ul
        %li
          You may choose a team more than once during the season.  You may choose any team that is playing in the current week.
        %li
          Thursday games: All Thursday games will be locked
          %span.red 1 hour
          %span before the kickoff of the first Thursday game.
        %li
          Sunday and Monday games: All Sunday and Monday games will be locked
          %span.red 1 hour
          %span before the first kickoff of the first Sunday game (excluding international games).
        %li
          International games: All International games will be locked
          %span.red 1 hour
          %span before the start of the first international game.
        %li
          Any pick not submitted prior to those deadlines automatically defaults to the first Monday night (MNF) home team.
        %li
          Picks must be submitted via the website at KOPOOL.org.
          %span.red I have NO access to anyone's login credentials and therefore cannot make picks for you.
          %span 
        %li
          Once your pick is submitted, you may change it as long as your change occurs before the weekly deadlines as described above.
        %li
          All picks will remain confidential until the picks for the week are posted on the website.
